    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/ac310ccda91cb5f6dd327822837f57f9.poster.avif?t=1743490744\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/ac310ccda91cb5f6dd327822837f57f9.webm?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/ac310ccda91cb5f6dd327822837f57f9.mp4?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>]在这个游戏中，你会得到一把锤子和一个沉重的球，比赛只有一个目标：把球投进洞里。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/006ebf659ce37e08950687ffb2c1d44a.poster.avif?t=1743490744\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/006ebf659ce37e08950687ffb2c1d44a.webm?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/006ebf659ce37e08950687ffb2c1d44a.mp4?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>[控制方法]<br>用任何方法把球推入洞中，即使您不熟悉VR游戏，您也可以通过摆动锤子来享受【一锤进洞】！<br>有时候，球并不像你想要的那样滚动，控制击球力度和设定球的方向将极大地帮助你达到目标。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/1211e8e846b7c14a6b21c0ac4d4283d1.poster.avif?t=1743490744\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/1211e8e846b7c14a6b21c0ac4d4283d1.webm?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/1211e8e846b7c14a6b21c0ac4d4283d1.mp4?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>[简单可爱的地图]<br>游戏地图由可爱的立方块组成，简单而充满活力的色彩，让人不会厌倦，重复体验!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/f68b3bb3fc71420ae2ff8837206fd529.poster.avif?t=1743490744\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/f68b3bb3fc71420ae2ff8837206fd529.webm?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197470/extras/f68b3bb3fc71420ae2ff8837206fd529.mp4?t=1743490744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>[难度提升]<br>一旦你完成了每个阶段，你将经历更困难的阶段，甚至更多的障碍。<br>从平地，到上坡，下坡，木板，跳坡或熔岩，有时这些地形是有利的，但它们也会给你带来麻烦；<br>不同材质的立方块会有不同的阻力，把握好特点，挥动锤子滚动球以获得最佳结果！<br>无论是用力击球还是轻轻击球，是否使用特殊的方块或物体，你都是这个游戏的探路者！",
